\par
\lquote\i Splitting of the Ego in the efensive Process\rquote\i0\par
\pard\fi720\li567\sl360\slmult1\qj 1941 \i Int. J. Psycho-Anal\i0 ., 22 (1), 65-8. (Trad. de   James Strachey.)\par
